'''Fëanorian''' can refer to:

*The '''[[House of Fëanor]]''', whose members were '''[[Fëanor]]''' himself, his [[Sons of Fëanor|Seven Sons]] and their followers.
*The Feanorian script, more usually known as the '''''[[Tengwar]]'''''.
*The '''[[Fëanorian dialect]]''' of the [[Noldor]] in [[East Beleriand|East-Beleriand]].
*The '''[[Fëanorian lamps]]''', a rare Noldorin artifact.
